                "invention-title": [
                    "Zero-carbon-emission hydrogen ammonia electric fusion steel rolling heating furnace system and control method",
                    "一种零碳排放的氢氨电融合轧钢加热炉系统及控制方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen ammonia electric fusion steel rolling heating furnace system with zero carbon emission and a control method. Comprising a liquid ammonia storage tank, an electronic flow valve, a vaporizer, a decomposing furnace, a variable frequency fan, a burner gas distribution system, a burner, an electric radiant tube, a condenser, a chimney and the like. After liquid ammonia is vaporized by the vaporizer, one part of ammonia gas is directly distributed to the combustor for combustion through the combustor gas distribution system, the other part of ammonia gas is catalytically decomposed into nitrogen and hydrogen through the decomposing furnace, then the nitrogen and the hydrogen are distributed to the combustor for combustion through the combustor gas distribution system, and the hydrogen is inflammable, high in combustion speed and high in heat value compared with the ammonia gas. Ammonia gas can be driven to stably ignite and combust; the heating furnace has the advantages that the preheating section uses the electric radiant tube for heating, use of green electricity on the steel rolling heating furnace can be increased, hydrogen and ammonia mixed combustion is used in the heating section and the soaking section, the problems that ignition is difficult and the combustion speed is low due to the fact that ammonia is singly used are solved, and the heating furnace has great significance in improving comprehensive utilization of ammonia energy."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种零碳排放的氢氨电融合轧钢加热炉系统及控制方法。包括液氨储存罐、电子流量阀、汽化器、分解炉、可变频风机、燃烧器配气系统、燃烧器、电辐射管、冷凝器和烟囱等。液氨经汽化器汽化后一部分氨气直接经由燃烧器配气系统配送到燃烧器燃烧，另一部分氨气通过分解炉催化分解为氮气和氢气，然后经由燃烧器配气系统配送到燃烧器燃烧，氢气相对于氨气易燃、燃烧速度快和热值高，能带动氨气稳定着火燃烧；本发明的优点在于预热段使用电辐射管加热，可加大绿电在轧钢加热炉上的使用，加热段和均热段使用氢气和氨气混合燃烧，解决了单一使用氨气着火难和燃烧速度慢的问题，对提高氨能源的综合利用具有重要意义。"
                }
            ]
